 A judge sentenced a former TSA agent to six months in jail for secretly videotaping a female co-worker while she was in the bathroom .
prosecutors say the agent , 33-year-old Daniel Boykin , entered the woman 's home multiple times .
Police found more than 90 videos and 1,500 photos of the victim on Boykin 's phone and computer .
Police says case was one of the worst invasion of privacy cases .